But you killed my father.

51
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:08,480
Between us,

52
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:10,320
there can never be peace.

53
00:03:10,410 --> 00:03:16,300
♪Nurturing a restless flame
with silence♪

54
00:03:16,630 --> 00:03:22,530
♪Even if my palms burn, I won't give in♪

55
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,840
An Ning is in my hands.

56
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:09,840
If you want to save her, come alone.

57
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:11,360
Don't play tricks.

58
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:13,240
You know what I'm capable of.

59
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,320
You can't beat Huo Xiao,

60
00:04:41,320 --> 00:04:42,600
so you take your anger out on me.

61
