I'd go after Huo Xiao's weak spot.

63
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,840
That's the only way to take him down.

64
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:51,040
As for the method,

65
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:51,720
it doesn't really matter.

66
