Jiang Meng,
come at me if you have the guts!

101
00:06:10,760 --> 00:06:11,720
Fine.

102
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:13,840
Then get on your knees.

103
00:06:13,840 --> 00:06:15,160
Beg me like a dog.

104
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:16,840
Maybe once I've cooled down,

105
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:18,560
I'll show some mercy.

106
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:20,360
Let her live a bit longer.

107
