Dad.

125
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:17,760
Didn't we agree

126
00:09:17,760 --> 00:09:20,040
to spare An Ning's life?

127
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:22,560
Spare her for what?

128
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:24,400
Who cares about
that transfer agreement now?

129
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:25,600
Just kill her first.

130
00:09:27,560 --> 00:09:29,040
To get released on bail,

131
00:09:29,040 --> 00:09:31,320
I gave the higher-ups
30% of the profits.

132
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,880
Anyone standing in my way

133
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:34,200
has no way out.

134
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:35,920
The situation's already set.

135
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:37,600
Let's go.

136
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:39,240
Don't get stained with this mess.

137
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,000
Let's go.

138
00:09:45,760 --> 00:09:47,240
You crawl so fast.

139
